caption: Their salad and shrimp quesadilla is delicious!  The guys who cook are really great chefs!
Food and smoothies are awesome, the staff behind the counter can be a little more friendlier.
They gave me bacon egg and cheese for free
Services are so great And the staff are interested in doing the best and in a wonderful way The food is clean and delicious Clean's on top of it And drinks and juice and food are clean and delicious

Everytime in the mornings I get the same drink 2 or 3 drinks. I Always get charged a different price. I bring it the guy in the morning attention at the register. He's telling me it's one price before and when I get overcharged it's that price now. Every person that has made me this drink has charged me the same price until these past few days with this other guy. The guy behind the counter always taking his sweet time away from the register and when it's time to pay you end up waiting for him to come checkout your items. I always have to make him aware that I am trying to pay. They need a better system and their employees need to know the prices of the items they are selling. I have been a loyal customer since the store has open me and my family. The quality of service is not the same as it once was.
Very nice, well managed store...
TERRIBLE service, these people cannot follow simple instructions and they do not care if they mess up your order! Will never buy from here again!!!

I placed an order with this establishment on GrubHub, after which the order was immediately cancelled for no clear reason. My payment method was still charged. I called and spoke with someone who answered the phone and they were extremely ruda.  I would not recommend this place to anyone, especially since they have such random items along with food items such as medicine and condoms. what kind of restaurant with delivery service offers condoms as an option?

The food is fresh here and the place seems to be very clean. I love the salads. My only problem with this place is the little guy that runs the salad bar in the evenings. I complained once about the chicken cutlet that was put into my salad being burnt. I still paid for the salad but the chicken was burnt and the little guy was seriously not interested in my complaint which i feel was valid because the chicken was burnt. That was a few weeks ago. I went back this evening to get a salad and the little guy says there's no chicken cutlet. While i actually saw that the was chicken cutlet (because i checked the window in the back before i ordered the salad.) To me this just proves either personal profiling or bad service on another level. I like this place I live and work in this neighborhood I will no longer be patronizing this establishment due to the bad service on the little guys part and no action taken by management. As tenant association president of my building I will emplore my neighbors not to patronize an establishment that would profile who they deem not worthy of good service. ... and they're 20 other stores in the neighborhood that appreciates all their patrons, not just the gentrified ones. Not cool👎
The best deli in Harlem. Quality selection of products and helpful staff.
I love the smoothies and the service is good. The servers are funny and friendly.

Healthy Choice is my favorite place to go to grab my smoothie after a workout session. The staff are all hospitable and pleasant and the deli is always so clean and the food is so fresh. It has been recommended to all my fellow kickboxers including the instructors and they love it! - So if you’re in the neighborhood stop by and grab something to eat or drink!

Excellent customer service! I love coming here. Everyone is super nice.  Many people in the neighborhood come to the store to buy Smoothies.   They are one of the few stores that’s actually have healthy choices.
amazing custom made salads and snack choices! the employees are incredibly helpful and friendly, as well.

I've wanted to write a review on Healthy Choice for a while now but I held off because their a new business in the area and I wanted to wait for them time to establish themself first. But after multiple incidents I've had here it's obvious these guys don't care. Sad really because stores constantly come and go and they are no exception. Tonight I tried to recover a double charge on my CC for a sand which I ordered last week. I showed the clerk the double charge on my card and he told me to come back tomorrow to fix. I told him I don't have time to come back tomorrow and he moved on to the next customer. Mind you I frequent here routinely and as a neighborhood store the level of professionalism is extremely poor. So I had to sit on hold with my bank to rectify the situation. ALSO multiple times I've ordered a burger and fries exact to the description on their menu and the cook(s) leave something off or don't follow directions. I have left tips too and I regret it because they don't care. In fact when you try to talk to them about it they still ask you what you want on your order and will still not get it right. Maybe they can't read the menu, ok fine but then listen to the customer and if you still can't understand it then write it down instead of being rude when I hand it back to you to fix. These guys really need an attitude adjustment, I just can't with this place anymore!
Terrible service my chop cheese wasn’t fully cooked and they don’t have certain drinks,sandwiches,or chips if I were u I’ll simply walk down to the store closest to the park

The cashier throws a sandwich at me because I wasn’t able to afford it... I even stated that I wasn’t gonna pay for and I walk away..as soon as I turn away the cashier throws the sandwich that I ordered at me... the store owner and workers all followed me out the store right after as if they was gonna jump me.. then the workers started to call me the N word and cursed me out...I definitely don’t consider anyone going to this store especially if your a person of color..they seem very racist and was very disrespectful towards me and I’m looking to sue them very soon.

They consistently try to give me less change than what I am owed. Especially if you order the smoothie. It says $4 on the screen but they have tried to charge me $6.50 on three separate occasions. Beware .

For a new store that still has big gaps in their stock, the counter dude needs to work on his greeting, as in there wasn't one. Sorry to interrupt your whole lot of nothing going on, but speaking when spoken to is Step 1 in Customer Service.  As I make my way to the back thru a maze of open boxes, I'm curious as to why they aren't more fully stocked. They've been open too long to have such gaps in the Snapple case. The deli portion seems rearing to go. If I wanted coffee, there's a nice station by the door with packaged baked goods. But all I got was the runner-up fruit punch Snapple.  I'm in the area enough, so I will try again, but right now it's a shiny, marble-topped meh.

This store is relatively new to the east harlem neighborhood. Its clean and well taken care of. The staff are friendly and helpful. While the prices are a bit high for this neighborhood there are not many stores like this in this area. They have a fairly large made to order salad bar. They also have a wide variety of freshly made juices and healthy made to order drinks. They also have hot and cold made to order sandwiches. Not to mention large organic selection of drinks. If ur looking for a healthy juice or healthy salad then pay this one of a few stores like this in the east harlem area. But be prepared to pay a little more for your items but it is definitely worth a visit.

Love this spot they cook really good food and have the best smoothies! They have really good customer service especially the guy behind the register I believe his name is Omar.  I will definitely continue to come to this store weekly! Keep up the good work 😉
Outstanding choice lol Best sandwich for you bucks
They talk too much...the guy took about 15 min to make an acai bowl...
My grill chicken salad had a bone. Not good, I decided to still give 4 stars because my family likes this place.  I just hope every one there continue to give there best In everything to customers.

I work in the area and always get my Smoothie from here and sometimes lunch. I call ahead of time for my order. Very friendly staff and my order is always ready on time! Thank you!--- written 6 months ago and gave them a 5 star rating.  Current review--  I work in the area and sometimes even  after a few disappointments from here. I get a cold turkey sandwich and a smoothie from here for lunch. I ignored it the first few times, but this was the last time I was going to get this repeated service.  I am now changing my 5 star rating to now a 1. The bread roll is hard and dry, very difficult to bite into. The cheddar cheese is dry on the edges and some towards the inside. I asked for extra mayo and barely any mayo. The lettuce is old and color changed. The person I gave the order too, told me they serve medium size smoothies, but I got a small smoothie. If you don't have it , then just say we don't have it. Do not charge me for something and give me something else.  When I called the shop back because I was very upset, the the person who answered the phone said "what can I do for you then?".. rude.. I told them I was not going to be coming back to get another sandwich but this is not the way to do service. He said "ok the next time you come.." I cut him off and told him I was not going to return again because of repeated disappointments. He said "ok".. as if he didn't care....  Very disappointing. Bad customer service.  I will not be coming back to this location. Thank you for the treatment.

This is one of a kind excellently healthy source of really good food and drinks. Very courteous customer service and pretty fast too! Whenever am back in Harlem, I’ll be back for sure. I love this place, try the King Kong smoothie for a size.
a regular here.. come here like 3 times a day. love the customer service and employees.
Great store. A little pricey for Harlem residents but great food and choices.
Fresh food, delicious smoothie all day, staff is friendly very nice place to grab lunch...what more could u ask for!👍
